    "We see that the monthly mean excess return positive.\n",
    "\n",
    "##\n",
    "Now we construct a universe of N=50 synthetic assets which follow the single factor model:\n",
    "**Single Asset Return Process**\n",
    "$$\\tilde{r}_{i,t} = \\beta_i \\tilde{r}_{m,t} + \\varepsilon_{i,t}, \\qquad \\varepsilon_{i,t} \\overset{iid}{\\sim} \\mathcal{N}(0, \\sigma^2_{\\varepsilon,i}), \\quad i = 1, \\dots, N$$\n",
    "\n",
    "where $\\tilde{r}_{i,t}$ denotes the excess return on asset $i$.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Parameter Draws**\n",
    "$$\\beta_i \\overset{iid}{\\sim} \\text{Uniform}(0.5,\\ 1.5), \\qquad \\sigma_{\\varepsilon,i} \\overset{iid}{\\sim} \\text{Uniform}\\!\\left(\\frac{0.10}{\\sqrt{12}},\\ \\frac{0.30}{\\sqrt{12}}\\right)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**True Monthly Parameters**\n",
    "$$\\mu_i = \\beta_i \\hat{\\mu}_m, \\qquad \\Sigma = \\sigma^2_m \\beta\\beta' + \\text{diag}(\\sigma^2_\\varepsilon)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "where $\\beta = (\\beta_1, \\dots, \\beta_N)'$."
   ]
